| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-3002 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 1b61e4a1-b676-556a-9a4b-7389288b2c57"
